WEBVTT

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:38.240
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.390 --> 00:01:41.220
[Episode 14]

00:01:48.180 --> 00:01:48.710
Xuan.

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:49.870
Drink up.

00:01:50.130 --> 00:01:50.570
Okay.

00:01:50.950 --> 00:01:51.470
Honey,

00:01:51.979 --> 00:01:52.780
happy time.

00:01:53.710 --> 00:01:54.350
Wow.

00:01:54.720 --> 00:01:56.240
Honey, you're amazing.

00:01:58.110 --> 00:01:59.050
Which episode is this?

00:01:59.050 --> 00:01:59.740
Episode 4.

00:02:00.050 --> 00:02:01.910
Zhou Mingde hasn't found out yet?

00:02:02.310 --> 00:02:03.640
This woman is so wicked.

00:02:04.810 --> 00:02:05.670
Watch with me for a bit.

00:02:05.670 --> 00:02:06.000
Okay.

00:02:08.919 --> 00:02:10.050
It's from my sister.

00:02:11.270 --> 00:02:12.130
Hello, Sister.

00:02:13.710 --> 00:02:14.490
I didn't forget.

00:02:14.490 --> 00:02:14.800
We...

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.329
We'll go in a couple of days.

00:02:16.610 --> 00:02:17.670
Okay, don't worry.

00:02:17.820 --> 00:02:18.620
Alright. Bye.

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:20.800
Is everything okay?

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:21.360
It's okay.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:22.620
She asked us to go over.

00:02:24.760 --> 00:02:26.730
Princess, time to get up!

00:02:28.570 --> 00:02:30.480
Coming.

00:02:39.250 --> 00:02:40.450
It's still early!

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:41.410
Early?

00:02:41.410 --> 00:02:42.850
It's already afternoon.

00:02:43.520 --> 00:02:44.970
Your aunt called.

00:02:44.970 --> 00:02:46.230
She asked us to go over.

00:02:46.640 --> 00:02:47.450
I'm not going!

00:02:49.250 --> 00:02:49.990
Why not?

00:02:50.410 --> 00:02:53.250
We go every year.
It wouldn't be right to skip this year.

00:02:53.250 --> 00:02:53.640
I...

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:56.480
I have major courses this year.
Did you forget?

00:02:56.640 --> 00:02:57.200
Right.

00:02:58.140 --> 00:03:00.570
You just stay there for two days
and then come back.

00:03:00.570 --> 00:03:02.450
I have class tomorrow.

00:03:02.470 --> 00:03:03.500
Then let's go there
the day after tomorrow.

00:03:03.500 --> 00:03:04.130
Okay?

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:07.800
Dad, I really can't go this time.

00:03:07.800 --> 00:03:10.320
I have an interview for Professor Ye's
course when school starts.

00:03:10.320 --> 00:03:12.980
I'm practicing every day.
Every second counts.

00:03:13.280 --> 00:03:14.120
Yeah.

00:03:15.250 --> 00:03:17.800
How can I be at ease
leaving you home alone?

00:03:17.800 --> 00:03:19.970
You're so forgetful.

00:03:19.970 --> 00:03:21.300
You might even get lost.

00:03:21.920 --> 00:03:25.010
When we get there, I'll take you out
for something good, okay?

00:03:25.010 --> 00:03:25.530
Why...

00:03:25.690 --> 00:03:28.640
can't I stay home alone?

00:03:28.800 --> 00:03:30.480
I can just order takeout.

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:32.579
Takeout is so unhealthy.

00:03:32.970 --> 00:03:35.000
Alright. If she doesn't want to go,
don't push it.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:36.360
She goes there every year.

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.970
Skipping one year wouldn't matter.

00:03:37.970 --> 00:03:38.410
No...

00:03:38.570 --> 00:03:39.079
It's just...

00:03:39.079 --> 00:03:40.250
Takeout is unhealthy.

00:03:40.250 --> 00:03:41.640
And she can't cook.

00:03:43.850 --> 00:03:45.480
Xiaole can cook.

00:03:46.970 --> 00:03:47.900
What's it to you?

00:03:50.450 --> 00:03:51.410
I'll call Tong.

00:03:52.020 --> 00:03:53.850
You're staying at Xiaole's place.

00:03:53.850 --> 00:03:54.200
No...

00:03:54.730 --> 00:03:56.260
Are you really calling him?

00:04:14.130 --> 00:04:16.760
Dad, I really can manage on my own.

00:04:16.760 --> 00:04:19.250
-What can you do?
-Don't ask him to come. I'm not going.

00:04:19.250 --> 00:04:19.850
You can't!

00:04:20.640 --> 00:04:22.079
I really can.

00:04:22.079 --> 00:04:22.810
Cut the crap.

00:04:23.080 --> 00:04:23.690
Mr. Yi.

00:04:24.370 --> 00:04:25.570
Xiaole, you're here.

00:04:26.130 --> 00:04:26.890
For the next few days,

00:04:26.890 --> 00:04:28.370
I'll leave her in your care.

00:04:28.370 --> 00:04:29.400
Your dad told you, right?

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:29.760
Yeah.

00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:30.200
And

00:04:30.450 --> 00:04:31.100
remember:

00:04:31.250 --> 00:04:32.130
don't let her wander off,

00:04:32.130 --> 00:04:33.390
don't let her get hurt,

00:04:33.570 --> 00:04:35.520
and pick her up
and drop her off for class.

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:36.200
Don't worry, Mr. Yi.

00:04:36.200 --> 00:04:38.010
My parents and I
will take good care of her.

00:04:38.010 --> 00:04:38.570
I object!

00:04:38.890 --> 00:04:39.690
I object!

00:04:40.340 --> 00:04:42.140
If you object, then come with me.

00:04:43.250 --> 00:04:45.510
He definitely doesn't want this either.

00:04:45.760 --> 00:04:46.270
Mr. Yi,

00:04:46.570 --> 00:04:47.960
if Yi Lan doesn't stay at my place,

00:04:47.960 --> 00:04:49.050
I'll report to you immediately.

00:04:49.050 --> 00:04:50.780
Then you can come take her away.

00:04:51.750 --> 00:04:52.810
It's settled then.

00:04:53.490 --> 00:04:53.970
Lan,

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:55.850
take good care of yourself.

00:04:56.760 --> 00:04:57.130
Bye.

00:04:57.810 --> 00:04:58.450
Let's go.

00:04:58.690 --> 00:04:59.820
-Uncle Dong, take care.
-Lan.

00:04:59.820 --> 00:05:00.320
-Okay.
-Bye.

00:05:00.320 --> 00:05:00.890
Bye, Mrs. Yi.

00:05:00.890 --> 00:05:01.200
Bye.

00:05:15.640 --> 00:05:16.750
Just go home.

00:05:17.010 --> 00:05:18.540
I'll be fine here by myself.

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:21.400
Oh.

00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:25.840
Mr. Yi!

00:05:26.490 --> 00:05:28.100
Yi Lan said I should...

00:05:28.250 --> 00:05:28.840
Come back.

00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:30.510
She said you should take care

00:05:30.640 --> 00:05:31.490
and stay safe!

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:40.010
Then

00:05:40.320 --> 00:05:41.780
I'll go pack your luggage.

00:05:43.450 --> 00:05:44.010
No need.

00:05:45.640 --> 00:05:46.640
I'll do it myself.

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:09.160
Are my shoes still there?

00:06:10.250 --> 00:06:10.610
Yeah.

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:17.920
It's not like it's your first time here.

00:06:50.810 --> 00:06:52.840
S-Staying at your place is fine,

00:06:53.320 --> 00:06:54.890
but we need to set three ground rules.

00:06:54.890 --> 00:06:56.220
Stay out of my business.

00:06:56.320 --> 00:06:58.650
I couldn't care less about your business.

00:06:58.930 --> 00:07:00.530
What are the other two rules?

00:07:01.050 --> 00:07:02.160
I haven't thought of them yet.

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:03.420
I'll tell you when I do.

00:07:12.450 --> 00:07:12.980
Where...

00:07:13.930 --> 00:07:14.960
Where do I sleep?

00:07:22.080 --> 00:07:23.880
I don't want to sleep in your bed.

00:07:23.930 --> 00:07:25.580
Well, if you don't sleep in my room,

00:07:25.580 --> 00:07:28.050
are you planning to sleep
in my parents' room?

00:07:28.050 --> 00:07:30.850
Where would they sleep
when they get back tonight?

00:07:37.720 --> 00:07:38.840
Look at this mess!

00:07:46.890 --> 00:07:47.810
I just woke up.

00:07:47.810 --> 00:07:49.470
It's normal for it to be messy.

00:07:50.130 --> 00:07:52.810
And my dad keeps praising you
for being tidy.

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:08.550
Well, should I take off
your duvet cover first?

00:08:10.640 --> 00:08:11.700
What are you doing?

00:08:11.890 --> 00:08:13.720
Didn't I say I'm changing it to mine?

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:14.100
Well,

00:08:14.760 --> 00:08:16.010
do you even know how to take it off?

00:08:16.010 --> 00:08:16.890
Of course I do!

00:08:16.890 --> 00:08:17.320
Move aside!

00:08:17.320 --> 00:08:20.050
-Just go back to get your duvet first.
-Right now.

00:08:31.720 --> 00:08:32.650
Rule number two:

00:08:33.130 --> 00:08:34.580
no physical contact.

00:08:41.330 --> 00:08:43.440
I... I'll go back to get my sheets.

00:09:40.730 --> 00:09:42.060
What are you looking at?

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:45.300
You aren't looking for photos of yourself,
are you?

00:09:45.610 --> 00:09:46.330
No.

00:09:50.850 --> 00:09:51.520
I...

00:09:51.520 --> 00:09:52.990
need to head out for my class later.

00:09:52.990 --> 00:09:54.950
Can you give me a key to your place?

00:09:55.490 --> 00:09:57.560
No need. I'll be home all day today.

00:09:59.160 --> 00:10:01.010
What if you're not here tomorrow?

00:10:01.010 --> 00:10:01.680
Tomorrow?

00:10:02.890 --> 00:10:05.220
We'll worry about tomorrow when it comes.

00:10:05.520 --> 00:10:07.180
What time is your class later?

00:10:07.610 --> 00:10:08.400
4 PM.

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:09.850
Oh.

00:10:13.090 --> 00:10:14.010
It's already 3:30 PM.

00:10:14.010 --> 00:10:14.920
3:30 PM?

00:10:15.490 --> 00:10:17.330
Then get out. I need to change.

00:10:29.490 --> 00:10:30.610
You only have 20 minutes left.

00:10:30.610 --> 00:10:32.170
You won't make it by bus.

00:10:32.250 --> 00:10:33.510
Even if you take a taxi,

00:10:33.970 --> 00:10:35.700
you'll probably still be late.

00:10:36.400 --> 00:10:38.250
Can I borrow your e-bike?

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:46.610
You're seriously going

00:10:46.610 --> 00:10:48.940
to ride my e-bike with something that big?

00:10:55.130 --> 00:10:56.530
I'll just give you a lift.

00:11:00.010 --> 00:11:00.610
Thanks.

00:11:02.170 --> 00:11:03.590
Hurry up.

00:11:05.210 --> 00:11:06.010
Open the door.

00:11:14.610 --> 00:11:15.490
Me first.

00:11:15.490 --> 00:11:16.070
Why?

00:11:16.130 --> 00:11:17.690
This is my room now.

00:11:17.730 --> 00:11:18.520
This is still my house.

00:11:18.520 --> 00:11:19.760
You're just staying here temporarily.

00:11:19.760 --> 00:11:21.360
Move aside. I got here first!

00:11:22.130 --> 00:11:23.760
I've already got one foot in.

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:24.490
Who got here first?

00:11:24.490 --> 00:11:25.220
I don't care.

00:11:25.370 --> 00:11:26.250
Ladies first.

00:11:31.640 --> 00:11:32.490
Yi Lan...

00:11:43.130 --> 00:11:44.590
Mom, Yi Lan is bullying me.

00:11:47.010 --> 00:11:47.520
Xiaole.

00:11:47.850 --> 00:11:49.850
Your dad and I got held up on the road.

00:11:49.980 --> 00:11:51.640
We won't be back for a few days.

00:11:52.130 --> 00:11:52.930
What's wrong?

00:11:53.010 --> 00:11:55.010
Is Lan settling in okay at our place?

00:11:56.040 --> 00:11:57.090
Everything is fine.

00:11:57.090 --> 00:11:57.840
Don't worry, Mom.

00:11:57.840 --> 00:11:58.850
Then take good care of her.

00:11:58.850 --> 00:11:59.860
Okay, got it.

00:12:00.520 --> 00:12:01.380
What happened?

00:12:03.610 --> 00:12:04.730
My mom said

00:12:05.370 --> 00:12:07.230
they aren't coming back tonight.

00:12:07.490 --> 00:12:08.310
How about

00:12:08.970 --> 00:12:09.370
I

00:12:09.640 --> 00:12:11.300
take you to your aunt's place?

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:12.090
No!

00:12:13.250 --> 00:12:15.400
We agreed you'd stay out of my affairs.

00:12:17.330 --> 00:12:19.330
Get up. You're filthy!

00:12:21.330 --> 00:12:22.610
Like I'd even care.

00:12:35.730 --> 00:12:36.730
So noisy.

00:12:37.740 --> 00:12:39.580
When did he get so weird?

00:13:06.130 --> 00:13:06.640
Hello.

00:13:07.490 --> 00:13:08.080
Dad.

00:13:09.400 --> 00:13:10.140
What's up?

00:13:10.490 --> 00:13:11.550
You look like you're in a bad mood.

00:13:11.550 --> 00:13:12.350
What's wrong?

00:13:12.610 --> 00:13:13.400
Nothing.

00:13:13.520 --> 00:13:14.260
I'm fine.

00:13:14.780 --> 00:13:15.910
I just took a shower.

00:13:16.250 --> 00:13:17.520
Where are you?

00:13:17.640 --> 00:13:19.500
Where are Xiaole and his parents?

00:13:20.440 --> 00:13:21.490
Xiaole...

00:13:21.610 --> 00:13:22.790
is right next to me.

00:13:23.850 --> 00:13:24.570
Look.

00:13:27.730 --> 00:13:28.390
Uncle Dong.

00:13:29.610 --> 00:13:30.340
Don't worry.

00:13:30.400 --> 00:13:31.430
I just cooked for her.

00:13:31.430 --> 00:13:34.090
She ate two big bowls
and said it was really good.

00:13:35.130 --> 00:13:36.090
Thank you.

00:13:36.210 --> 00:13:37.040
No problem.

00:13:37.330 --> 00:13:38.800
I have to go now.

00:13:38.930 --> 00:13:39.330
Okay.

00:13:39.370 --> 00:13:39.730
All right.

00:13:39.730 --> 00:13:40.330
Bye, Uncle Dong.

00:13:40.330 --> 00:13:41.370
Bye, Dad.

00:13:41.520 --> 00:13:42.130
Good night.

00:13:42.130 --> 00:13:43.210
Bye.

00:13:43.250 --> 00:13:44.010
Good night.

00:13:46.090 --> 00:13:46.550
Xiaole.

00:13:46.970 --> 00:13:47.700
It's so late,

00:13:47.760 --> 00:13:49.620
and you're with your girlfriend?

00:13:50.210 --> 00:13:52.270
You were saying hello to her parents?

00:13:52.490 --> 00:13:53.490
You two made up?

00:13:54.590 --> 00:13:55.790
Don't talk nonsense.

00:13:56.250 --> 00:13:57.760
I'm out. You guys have fun.

00:14:03.010 --> 00:14:04.290
Can we talk?

00:14:07.280 --> 00:14:08.850
About what?

00:14:09.890 --> 00:14:11.980
Why have you been avoiding me?

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:17.490
I've been avoiding you?

00:14:19.250 --> 00:14:20.490
You're the one who has been avoiding me.

00:14:20.490 --> 00:14:22.130
How dare you accuse me first!

00:14:22.850 --> 00:14:25.680
Not only did you stop calling
and reaching out to me,

00:14:25.680 --> 00:14:26.490
but you also

00:14:26.970 --> 00:14:28.970
got yourself other female friends.

00:14:29.490 --> 00:14:32.250
I have other female friends?

00:14:34.400 --> 00:14:35.080
Yes.

00:14:37.090 --> 00:14:38.090
After everything

00:14:39.850 --> 00:14:41.400
you said to me before,

00:14:42.730 --> 00:14:44.010
you fell

00:14:46.330 --> 00:14:48.060
for someone else that quickly?

00:14:53.370 --> 00:14:54.090
I didn't.

00:14:55.250 --> 00:14:55.910
Then you...

00:14:59.800 --> 00:15:00.640
Never mind.

00:15:55.130 --> 00:15:56.590
I'm going to take a shower.

00:16:21.710 --> 00:16:26.990
