00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:53.130
Tong Xiaole, why do you have this photo...

00:16:59.680 --> 00:17:02.410
Are you just going
to keep staring at me like that?

00:17:20.369 --> 00:17:22.630
Hurry up and wash up. Breakfast is ready.

