00:19:14.940 --> 00:19:17.690
♪ You are everything I want ♪

00:19:48.770 --> 00:19:50.170
I'll go get you some milk.

00:21:01.850 --> 00:21:04.610
Xiaole, you're going out
to take photos this afternoon, right?

00:21:04.610 --> 00:21:07.570
I'm free today.
If you need an assistant, let me know.

00:21:15.160 --> 00:21:15.810
Sure.

00:21:15.890 --> 00:21:16.850
Then this afternoon...

00:21:16.850 --> 00:21:19.510
You're going out to take photos
this afternoon?

00:21:20.440 --> 00:21:22.130
Today's shooting schedule is pretty heavy.

00:21:22.130 --> 00:21:23.990
I probably can't handle it alone.

00:21:24.130 --> 00:21:25.440
I can help you.

00:21:26.770 --> 00:21:27.130
You?

00:21:27.850 --> 00:21:28.330
Yeah.

00:21:28.770 --> 00:21:29.330
Why

00:21:29.370 --> 00:21:31.100
do you suddenly want to help me?

00:21:33.370 --> 00:21:34.430
I'm short of money.

00:21:41.440 --> 00:21:42.810
Manman, sorry.

00:21:43.200 --> 00:21:45.810
I already have an assistant
for this afternoon.

00:21:45.810 --> 00:21:46.610
Thank you.

00:21:59.200 --> 00:21:59.600
Right.

00:22:00.050 --> 00:22:01.710
Dude, put the peace sign down.

00:22:02.610 --> 00:22:03.660
Look at my camera.

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:07.560
Dude, can you put your arm
around her shoulder?

00:22:07.570 --> 00:22:07.970
Right.

00:22:09.640 --> 00:22:10.370
Beautiful.

00:22:10.530 --> 00:22:12.590
Miss, could you rest your hand on him?

00:22:14.810 --> 00:22:15.370
Not like that.

00:22:15.370 --> 00:22:15.770
Yi Lan!

00:22:16.130 --> 00:22:16.770
Come here.

00:22:17.720 --> 00:22:18.920
Miss, just like this.

00:22:19.050 --> 00:22:20.770
Rest your hand on his shoulder.

00:22:20.770 --> 00:22:21.110
Yes.

00:22:21.130 --> 00:22:23.790
Dude, wrap your arm
around her waist naturally.

00:22:24.530 --> 00:22:26.820
Then look into her eyes.

00:22:27.130 --> 00:22:27.810
Right.

00:22:28.160 --> 00:22:29.020
Just like that!

00:22:29.370 --> 00:22:30.030
Fill light.

00:22:34.570 --> 00:22:34.890
So beautiful.

00:22:34.890 --> 00:22:36.640
That jawline is simply perfect.

00:22:36.640 --> 00:22:37.050
One,

00:22:37.050 --> 00:22:37.370
two,

00:22:37.370 --> 00:22:37.770
three.

00:22:39.770 --> 00:22:40.330
Great.

00:22:40.530 --> 00:22:41.330
One more shot.

00:23:29.810 --> 00:23:30.940
Listen to this song.

00:23:38.590 --> 00:23:42.510
♪ You make me forget
all the noise and chaos around me ♪

00:23:43.230 --> 00:23:46.820
♪ You fill my future
with so much fantasy ♪

00:23:47.790 --> 00:23:50.370
♪ With you by my side, I walk
through every morning and sunset ♪

00:23:50.370 --> 00:23:51.030
Don't move.

00:23:52.050 --> 00:23:52.210
Biscuit crumbs.

00:23:52.210 --> 00:23:55.910
♪ Just wanna share the ordinary days
with you ♪

00:23:56.200 --> 00:23:58.400
♪ My heart won't stop its racing beat ♪

00:23:58.760 --> 00:24:01.220
♪ The sweetness when our eyes meet ♪

00:24:01.690 --> 00:24:05.370
♪ Each time we meet,
it's as if the dream goes on ♪

00:24:05.760 --> 00:24:07.900
♪ How I wish to tell you ♪

00:24:08.030 --> 00:24:09.530
♪ It's not a coincidence or a miracle ♪

00:24:09.530 --> 00:24:10.000
Yi Lan.

00:24:12.370 --> 00:24:12.400
♪ It's destiny ♪

00:24:12.400 --> 00:24:13.090
You...

00:24:15.390 --> 00:24:17.240
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:17.260 --> 00:24:17.550
♪ Connecting you to my heartbeat ♪

00:24:17.550 --> 00:24:19.350
haven't fallen for me, have you?

00:24:19.460 --> 00:24:21.470
♪ Scrolling up and down the playlist ♪

00:24:21.640 --> 00:24:25.030
♪ Disrupting the rhythm of my breath ♪

00:24:25.190 --> 00:24:29.060
♪ On repeat, the song
tells the secret I can't speak ♪

00:24:29.120 --> 00:24:30.750
♪ The smile at the corner of your lips ♪

00:24:31.110 --> 00:24:31.480
♪ Makes me wonder ♪

00:24:31.480 --> 00:24:32.130
It's okay.

00:24:32.640 --> 00:24:33.370
Anyway,

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:34.440
♪ If Cupid's golden arrow
has finally found you ♪

00:24:34.440 --> 00:24:36.500
I've decided not to like you anymore.

00:24:38.730 --> 00:24:40.940
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:40.970 --> 00:24:43.160
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:43.230 --> 00:24:45.340
♪ Sharing with you ♪

00:24:45.410 --> 00:24:47.860
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:47.880 --> 00:24:52.390
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:52.460 --> 00:24:54.640
♪ Sharing with you ♪

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:56.620
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:57.010 --> 00:24:58.740
♪ Sharing my earbuds with you ♪

00:24:58.770 --> 00:25:00.810
♪ Connecting you to my heartbeat ♪

00:25:00.810 --> 00:25:02.090
Stop kissing!

00:25:03.290 --> 00:25:03.890
Dad!

00:25:03.960 --> 00:25:05.330
U-Uncle Dong.

00:25:05.610 --> 00:25:06.090
I...

00:25:09.640 --> 00:25:10.900
What are you two doing?

00:25:10.960 --> 00:25:12.620
Did you just kiss my daughter?

00:25:14.640 --> 00:25:16.030
Mr. Yi.

00:25:16.060 --> 00:25:17.530
Mr. Yi.

00:25:42.480 --> 00:25:43.050
Xiaole.

00:25:48.050 --> 00:25:49.720
Are you and Lan together now?

00:25:51.920 --> 00:25:52.570
Mom.

00:25:53.400 --> 00:25:55.070
Please don't ask about this.

00:25:55.160 --> 00:25:56.770
I can handle it myself.

00:26:03.370 --> 00:26:04.570
Tong, say something.

00:26:07.850 --> 00:26:10.250
I didn't expect
you would get a girlfriend.

00:26:12.440 --> 00:26:13.650
Lan is a nice girl.

00:26:14.850 --> 00:26:16.370
She's always cheerful.

00:26:18.920 --> 00:26:21.050
Our families know each other well too.

00:26:23.850 --> 00:26:24.580
That's good.

00:26:27.770 --> 00:26:29.370
It's just that Mr. Yi...

00:26:30.850 --> 00:26:32.250
This is really annoying.

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:40.090
What's really going on
between you and Xiaole?

00:26:40.090 --> 00:26:41.130
His parents weren't home.

00:26:41.130 --> 00:26:42.640
Why didn't you tell me?

00:26:44.830 --> 00:26:45.740
I'm furious.

00:26:48.330 --> 00:26:49.440
Are you two together?

00:26:49.440 --> 00:26:49.790
No...

00:26:52.090 --> 00:26:52.850
Not really.

00:26:52.920 --> 00:26:54.440
What do you mean by that?

00:26:54.440 --> 00:26:55.370
If you're not together,

00:26:55.370 --> 00:26:57.210
why were you two kissing?

00:26:58.000 --> 00:26:59.420
I'm going crazy!

00:26:59.720 --> 00:27:01.320
Did he take advantage of you?

00:27:01.770 --> 00:27:02.900
Did he force you?

00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:05.380
Fine, I'm going to ask him myself.

00:27:05.380 --> 00:27:05.680
Dad!

00:27:05.680 --> 00:27:06.810
Where are you going?

00:27:08.160 --> 00:27:09.440
Dad!

00:27:11.640 --> 00:27:12.530
How about...

00:27:14.440 --> 00:27:15.170
give it a try?

00:27:15.850 --> 00:27:17.330
Xiaole, tell us what you think.

00:27:17.330 --> 00:27:17.960
Well,

00:27:19.160 --> 00:27:19.920
about this,

00:27:20.240 --> 00:27:21.300
I'll listen to Dad.

00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:25.680
Mr. Yi

00:27:26.920 --> 00:27:28.130
brags about his daughter all day long,

00:27:28.130 --> 00:27:30.440
saying how great she is
and how well she plays the cello.

00:27:30.440 --> 00:27:31.470
He spoils her way too much.

00:27:31.470 --> 00:27:31.950
Yeah.

00:27:32.680 --> 00:27:33.540
In the future,

00:27:33.610 --> 00:27:34.600
our Xiaole

00:27:34.720 --> 00:27:37.050
is probably gonna have to put up
with a lot.

00:27:37.960 --> 00:27:38.440
Alright.

00:27:38.440 --> 00:27:39.320
Get ready.

00:27:39.440 --> 00:27:40.130
Mr. Yi

00:27:40.240 --> 00:27:41.440
will definitely be here any minute.

00:27:41.440 --> 00:27:41.900
Will he?

00:27:42.240 --> 00:27:42.940
Yeah.

00:27:43.640 --> 00:27:44.050
See?

00:27:44.440 --> 00:27:45.200
Go open the door.

00:27:45.200 --> 00:27:45.850
So soon.

00:27:47.770 --> 00:27:48.230
Xiaole.

00:27:48.400 --> 00:27:49.130
Come with me.

00:27:50.160 --> 00:27:51.620
Just follow my lead.

00:27:51.720 --> 00:27:52.650
Don't be scared.

00:27:55.850 --> 00:27:57.150
Coming.

00:27:57.440 --> 00:27:57.920
Easy, easy.

00:27:57.920 --> 00:27:58.720
Mr. Yi, come in.

00:27:58.720 --> 00:27:59.780
Please have a seat.

00:28:00.330 --> 00:28:00.730
Hurry.

00:28:00.890 --> 00:28:01.440
Lan.

00:28:01.530 --> 00:28:02.130
Have a seat.

00:28:02.130 --> 00:28:02.960
-Honey.
-Have a seat.

00:28:02.960 --> 00:28:03.670
Make some tea.

00:28:03.670 --> 00:28:04.770
I just made some good tea for you.

00:28:04.770 --> 00:28:05.170
Hurry.

00:28:05.530 --> 00:28:06.330
Serve the tea.

00:28:06.480 --> 00:28:07.610
I'll pass on the tea.

00:28:07.680 --> 00:28:08.370
Have a sip.

00:28:08.920 --> 00:28:09.970
Have some.

00:28:10.720 --> 00:28:11.940
As for this matter,

00:28:12.370 --> 00:28:13.630
I am also responsible.

00:28:13.680 --> 00:28:15.400
I shouldn't have let our Lan stay here.

00:28:15.400 --> 00:28:17.400
It caused you unnecessary trouble.

00:28:17.920 --> 00:28:19.120
But there is one thing

00:28:19.440 --> 00:28:20.440
I need to find out.

00:28:21.160 --> 00:28:21.920
Xiaole,

00:28:23.000 --> 00:28:24.480
what exactly are your feelings

00:28:24.480 --> 00:28:25.850
for our Lan?

00:28:28.370 --> 00:28:29.570
They are grown up now.

00:28:29.680 --> 00:28:30.400
As for their business,

00:28:30.400 --> 00:28:31.480
we should let them decide for themselves.

00:28:31.480 --> 00:28:32.100
We should

00:28:32.240 --> 00:28:33.040
stay out of it.

00:28:33.330 --> 00:28:34.000
Stay out of it.

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:35.930
You're telling me to stay out of it?

00:28:36.290 --> 00:28:37.770
My daughter has suffered so much.

00:28:37.770 --> 00:28:39.240
And you're telling me to stay out of it?

00:28:39.240 --> 00:28:40.750
Your words are out of line.

00:28:40.920 --> 00:28:42.140
Xiaole is my son.

00:28:42.440 --> 00:28:44.200
I know his character better than anyone.

00:28:44.200 --> 00:28:45.400
The way you're doubting him

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:47.260
clearly means you don't trust me.

00:28:49.370 --> 00:28:51.160
It's not that I don't trust you.

00:28:51.160 --> 00:28:52.560
And I'm not doubting him.

00:28:52.720 --> 00:28:53.780
Then... But our Lan

00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:55.800
would never make the first move.

00:28:56.160 --> 00:28:58.160
Xiaole must have taken advantage of her.

00:28:58.160 --> 00:28:59.420
My son is so excellent.

00:28:59.530 --> 00:29:00.920
What's wrong with Lan liking him?

00:29:00.920 --> 00:29:02.320
That's impossible!

00:29:02.440 --> 00:29:03.960
My daughter has never even been
in a relationship before!

00:29:03.960 --> 00:29:05.850
How could she possibly like him first?

00:29:05.850 --> 00:29:06.920
It was Lan who pursued him.

00:29:06.920 --> 00:29:07.920
I said it's impossible!

00:29:07.920 --> 00:29:09.920
Absolutely impossible!

00:29:10.440 --> 00:29:13.170
The two of them stayed alone together
for so long!

00:29:13.770 --> 00:29:15.480
A boy and a girl under one roof,

00:29:15.480 --> 00:29:18.090
who knows what Xiaole might have done?

00:29:18.160 --> 00:29:21.530
Who knows what could've happened?

00:29:21.680 --> 00:29:23.370
What are you doing?

00:29:23.370 --> 00:29:24.890
Nothing happened.

00:29:26.400 --> 00:29:27.400
Really? Nothing happened at all?

00:29:27.400 --> 00:29:28.160
Nothing!

00:29:28.890 --> 00:29:30.960
Mr. Yi, what are you doing?

00:29:32.400 --> 00:29:33.530
Calm down.

00:29:34.890 --> 00:29:36.420
Did you make the first move?

00:29:38.610 --> 00:29:39.290
Uncle Dong.

00:29:40.440 --> 00:29:42.320
I apologize to you and Lan.

00:29:43.090 --> 00:29:44.620
About what happened today,

00:29:44.640 --> 00:29:45.920
I was the one who made the first move.

00:29:45.920 --> 00:29:46.880
See that?

00:29:47.160 --> 00:29:47.640
Tong,

00:29:47.720 --> 00:29:49.200
he made the first move, right?

00:29:49.200 --> 00:29:49.480
Yes.

00:29:49.680 --> 00:29:50.850
Do you like our Lan?

00:29:52.480 --> 00:29:53.140
Uncle Dong.

00:29:55.480 --> 00:29:56.370
All this time,

00:29:57.160 --> 00:29:59.540
my feelings for Lan have been one-sided.

00:30:00.530 --> 00:30:02.400
But my feelings for Lan are real.

00:30:05.090 --> 00:30:06.420
Tong, did you hear that?

00:30:06.640 --> 00:30:07.540
One-sided.

00:30:07.850 --> 00:30:09.160
Do you know what "one-sided" means?

00:30:09.160 --> 00:30:10.130
One-sided.

00:30:11.610 --> 00:30:12.920
Xiaole, let me make this clear.

00:30:12.920 --> 00:30:14.040
Starting today,

00:30:14.200 --> 00:30:15.770
you are not allowed to see our Lan.

00:30:15.770 --> 00:30:16.570
Do you hear me?

00:30:18.330 --> 00:30:19.390
Let's go home, Lan.

00:30:26.610 --> 00:30:27.410
Let's go home.

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:41.730
Alright.

00:30:42.200 --> 00:30:43.600
You acted like a real man.

00:30:43.920 --> 00:30:45.110
But remember this:

00:30:45.720 --> 00:30:48.160
you have to take responsibility
for your actions.

00:30:48.160 --> 00:30:48.960
Do you hear me?

00:30:50.160 --> 00:30:50.850
Got it, Dad.